nodes.text: Wat Tambor and the Quest for the Sacred Eye of the Albino Cyclops
Wat Tambor and the Quest for the Sacred Eye of the Albino Cyclops is a 13-page comic featured in Star Wars: Visionaries, written and drawn by Michael Murnane.

In this Legends story, the Techno Union foreman Wat Tambor embarks on a transcendental quest to find a sacred artifact and to discover his fate. He is told to go to Mustafar in the end, where he will be killed.
